#### DAX Measures for this page

```dax
Direct User Violations = 
CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(FACT_RiskFindings), 
    FACT_RiskFindings[RiskType] = "Direct User Permission")

SoD Violations = 
CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(FACT_RiskFindings), 
    FACT_RiskFindings[RiskType] = "Segregation of Duties")

Excessive Privilege Findings = 
CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(FACT_RiskFindings), 
    FACT_RiskFindings[RiskType] = "Excessive Privileges")

Safes Without Manager = 
CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(FACT_RiskFindings), 
    FACT_RiskFindings[RiskType] = "No Safe Manager")

CPM Orphan Safes = 
CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(FACT_RiskFindings), 
    FACT_RiskFindings[RiskType] = "Orphaned CPM")

Admin Groups Compliance % = 
VAR _total = COUNTROWS(FACT_AdminAudit)
VAR _full = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(FACT_AdminAudit), 
    FACT_AdminAudit[PermissionLevel] = "Full")
RETURN DIVIDE(_full, _total, 0) * 100
```

